        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Reviewing Urban and Rural Adjustments to Level Hospital Expenses and Lopsided Payments Act of 2021 or the RURAL HELP Act of </b><b>2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to determine whether costs incurred by rural hospitals exceed costs incurred by urban hospitals under the Medicare inpatient prospective payment system and to adjust payments accordingly.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
